    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, but some people say the UN is basically just a tool for the big powers to keep control and that it's actually doing more harm than good by legitimizing certain regimes. is that just a fringe view or is there a serious academic argument for that?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
